title: 이달의소녀탐구 #132 (LOONA TV #132)
summary:
0:02 --PD Cho takes over and asks Kim Lip abou how she feels about going Gimcheon
for the MV shoot. Lip: “It is nothing compared to going out of the country.”
0:27 -- HeeJin: “The Gimcheon we are going to, apparently there are ghosts there. 👻"
Lip: “WHAT!? No way, that can’t be true…” (kinda scared)
0:50 -- They are ready to leave. Lip: “Let’s go!!!”
